replyTime":"2017-07-21T04:01:14.000Z","msg":"連登應該禁止用大學生ISP開Account<br />\n成日有中學雞大學雞係度亂吠<br />\n心都煩"},{"pid":"3c0ef4b4684d471520382330b95c56ab9b9a32c3","tid":329992,"uid":25758,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-21T04:03:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>做野最緊要人脈同工作經驗<br />\n<br />\n你都岩<br />\n但社會唔係只睇e兩點囉<br />\n<br />\n完<br />\n<br />\n智障，咁你讀唔讀呀<br />\n有degree有得升無degree無得升<br />\n讀唔讀？</blockquote><br />\n可以話你知，個社會就正正係剩係睇呢兩點"},{"pid":"63b6ecc1b8cbe66ace70ca95bfb837e7a9d9bb37","tid":329992,"uid":77143,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-21T04:10:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>做野最緊要人脈同工作經驗<br />\n<br />\n你都岩<br />\n但社會唔係只睇e兩點囉<br />\n<br />\n完<br />\n<br />\n智障，咁你讀唔讀呀<br />\n有degree有得升無degree無得升<br />\n讀唔讀？</blockquote><br />\n可以話你知，個社會就正正係剩係睇呢兩點</blockquote><br />\n頭五年學歷就緊係有用啦<br />\n五年之後工作經驗已經完全大過學歷<br />\n人脈就從來都係大哂嘅"},{"pid":"c2f2127ae635c460c015a8f9f87b796fbf8ac1de","tid":329992,"uid":35136,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-21T04:12:02.000Z","msg":"taught master就係搵錢<br />\nMPhil PhD就真係係求學問"},{"pid":"5e17ded11d40017627601fb0bababd5f0858e0aa","tid":329992,"uid":77180,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-21T04:18:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>以為有大學生個身份，<br />\n成功就近在咫尺？<br />\n個世界就跟住你轉？<br />\n就揾到大錢？<br />\n就入職大公司有好待遇？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n屌你咪撚傻啦<br />\n就算係三大<br />\n都咪撚發夢個學位幫到你<br />\n其他果d 咩恆大 鯨大就更加唔好講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n但你會比較多見到港大生畢業後<br />\n身光頸靚  前途一片光明咁<br />\n係因為入到港大既學生  多數有錢仔  有錢女<br />\n<br />\n依家見到d 人一味咁報 \bd  證書課程 , pt degree, master degree ...etc <br />\n心諗：成班傻閪黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n首先, for general搵工既話, ugrad 就夠用 <br />\n你讀多幾多個 master, 作用只係cv 加多一行, 表面野黎, 根本唔重要<br />\n做野最重要係人脈 同工作經驗<br />\n<br />\n其次係，有心讀書求學問<br />\n屌你，老實講<br />\n買參考書自己睇仲實際啦<br />\n真正吸收緊知識果陣，老實講就係自己拎住本書讀果陣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n上Lecture 真係多鳩如<br />\n<br />\n老老實實<br />\n根本所有大專院校都係一門生意<br />\n咩degree , master degree 都係賺你錢咋傻閪<br />\n其他咩hd asso 就更加係明賺你錢，賺到(笑)<br />\n你班傻仔讀完就以為自己係明日之星<br />\n<br />\n咪撚 on9啦</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n都好睇咩科<br />\n有好多科好難自學<br />\n垃圾文社科除外"},{"pid":"df10937ff9ab2733f6941ebad0f04b1fd62f8fa7","tid":329992,"uid":49603,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-21T04:22:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>講埋係人都知既野 仲以為自己好醒 有人脈有際遇都好 上到某d職級 係需要讀書攞張沙紙 下屬服你又好 跟返公司規矩又好 先可以升到你上去</blockquote><br />\n你先似係講埋係人都知既野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n事實係個個都有沙紙 點解要升你<br />\nGet到重點未"},{"pid":"3f74b49ce58bdacb4808c5b7d25c13258651a197","tid":329992,"uid":67551,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-21T04:22:23.000Z","msg":"唔會夠讀唔成書嗰啲黐線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n佢哋冇讀大學，出來幾年投身酒店、地產、保險 嗰堆，搵到快錢開始曬命<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 成日會有意無意曬下貴嘢，買股票贏幾多等等<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />永遠冇提衰嘢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />唔講以為佢係方展博<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e4c1e0f2c9652f4671796c64f67f0ace83145009","tid":329992,"uid":49603,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-21T04:23:45.000Z","msg":"正評左<br />\n香港實在太多人入到大學就打飛機串串貢<br />\n對未來社會有太多幻想<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b4a239f0cfcc2eb1b3b20134f412769be4105789","tid":329992,"uid":61653,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-21T04:24:46.000Z","msg":"駁唔到"},{"pid":"28a73cb93ea9cc413b259841a2ada4ce983495c4","tid":329992,"uid":60015,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-21T04:26:11.000Z","msg":"唔知你笑乜啦 <br />\n<br />\n讀書既野個個目的唔同<br />\n<br />\n政府工就全基本上係大學都一視同仁<br />\n升學就睇hon 話知你hku 定樹仁開大<br />\n<br />\n理論上 係Ou讀到first hon個人認為會比其他u既first hon更勁<br />\n<br />\n因為ou成績唔拉curve<br />\n過到3.5條線做first hon姐係你超過有一半學分係拎A 4.0<br />\n<br />\n而拎A係85分以上<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n利申：鯨大仔"},{"pid":"1f29f5a58fbe762c9d06f202dc61848898262cff","tid":329992,"uid":4596,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-21T04:26:36.000Z","msg":"我唔讀master升唔到職<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n利申:醫療科"},{"pid":"ec683b1ef03b2956fbadb6d8805b81d3eb16c089","tid":329992,"uid":126766,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-21T04:30:57.000Z","msg":"酸到<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0ecb7ba43669a3ae7f9947bb85f6113a85ce1667","tid":329992,"uid":115613,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-21T04:33:38.000Z","msg":"鯨大東大醫科degree勁過三大乞食科degree"},{"pid":"b385add16107c659d481dd0096d53a20cce04862","tid":329992,"uid":126238,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-21T04:37:09.000Z","msg":"樓豬酸酸的<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6c7bc5133f7389aad8de99c5a0701baaf88455e1","tid":329992,"uid":33751,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-21T04:42:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>首先,屌臭東大鯨大嘅風氣,由4月尾至6月中會達至高峰，<br />\n因為班dse面對放榜壓力無從發洩 <br />\n要搵人黎踩下定下個心 <br />\n6月中後會突然水盡鵝飛 <br />\n一黎怕自己會入，留條後路 <br />\n二黎開始迷信，想積下口德 <br />\n<br />\nDse放榜後，愁雲慘霧 <br />\n班小師弟見狀都唔敢亂屌 <br />\n所以由6月尾至8月 <br />\n情況相若，風氣極低位橫行，如經濟衰退一樣 <br />\n<br />\n到9月，開學兩三禮拜，新一屆dse仔開始有壓力，想搵人踩 <br />\nretake緊嘅又想有野俾佢增強信心，又踩 <br />\n讀緊asso ive 跟唔上o個班/讀得唔開心o既，又踩 <br />\n因此9月會有個小陽春，之後橫行，<br />\n12月至1月頭，同2月中，分別都會有個小陽春，因為有假放得閒，同考試迫近，<br />\n壓力愈來愈大，3月至4月頭會一直高位橫行 <br />\n<br />\n最後又到4月尾高峰 <br />\n年年都如是，歲歲皆如此 <br />\n<br />\n股市係咁就好囉屌你</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n屌你又講得幾啱<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n屌"},{"pid":"dd4fca3c925c9893a6bf756b1d5de8a704b16944","tid":329992,"uid":23385,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-21T04:51:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>唔會夠讀唔成書嗰啲黐線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n佢哋冇讀大學，出來幾年投身酒店、地產、保險 嗰堆，搵到快錢開始曬命<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 成日會有意無意曬下貴嘢，買股票贏幾多等等<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />永遠冇提衰嘢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />唔講以為佢係方展博<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n揾到快錢個班係可能冇有學歷個班長遠發展得咁好<br />\n但搵到快錢如果善用唔係鳩買野<br />\n正常係可以辛苦小幾年<br />\n不過搵到快錢係好似唔少人 但背後失敗既仲多<br />\n利申 搵到快錢買左樓 但想增值自己再轉行"},{"pid":"8a47b3ac72281291951726840b6eef934243010b","tid":329992,"uid":8009,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-21T05:02:01.000Z","msg":"識人東大ou畢業 六皮一個月<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"99658f2f9f701e06d05958a3b0958280249019b5","tid":329992,"uid":3764,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-21T05:08:34.000Z","msg":"見到你個post即刻lse master offer都reject埋<br />\nChing ho ball <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e475ee53bc3cc3afb226e2daccac8d38e0d9ffba","tid":329992,"uid":5151,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-21T05:10:07.000Z","msg":"其實係連登仔特別on9 又話fg無20k以上唔做 心諗你乜貨色呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 仲要有班傻既陪佢地一齊癲"},{"pid":"e53a617d7e3c947edc272fdd61e4e26db5792296","tid":329992,"uid":81234,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-21T05:23:42.000Z","msg":"唔知你笑咩啦"},{"pid":"e76c7cfe1bb28f917de341b5a91a2c6e2c2e555b","tid":329992,"uid":57378,"like":0,"