" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n你讀緊中學？</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/21/183654_67a546ccbfa6ec03d22d8c18060538b2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F21%2F183654_67a546ccbfa6ec03d22d8c18060538b2.jpg&h=362a2c7c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n好心做人唔好咁井底啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n淨係識8間大學？<br />\n同埋係masters 唔係master<br />\n唔知邊個井底<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你19歲入ibank?<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n24</blockquote><br />\n睇你個底就知啦<br />\n一時就19歲未溝到女<br />\n一時就老闆in人"},{"pid":"0fddc72fe2a79d71cfcb86ae6f24998976d5ad7a","tid":329992,"uid":23469,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-21T10:46:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>以為有大學生個身份，<br />\n成功就近在咫尺？<br />\n個世界就跟住你轉？<br />\n就揾到大錢？<br />\n就入職大公司有好待遇？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n屌你咪撚傻啦<br />\n就算係三大<br />\n都咪撚發夢個學位幫到你<br />\n其他果d 咩恆大 鯨大就更加唔好講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n但你會比較多見到港大生畢業後<br />\n身光頸靚  前途一片光明咁<br />\n係因為入到港大既學生  多數有錢仔  有錢女<br />\n<br />\n依家見到d 人一味咁報 \bd  證書課程 , pt degree, master degree ...etc <br />\n心諗：成班傻閪黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n首先, for general搵工既話, ugrad 就夠用 <br />\n你讀多幾多個 master, 作用只係cv 加多一行, 表面野黎, 根本唔重要<br />\n做野最重要係人脈 同工作經驗<br />\n<br />\n其次係，有心讀書求學問<br />\n屌你，老實講<br />\n買參考書自己睇仲實際啦<br />\n真正吸收緊知識果陣，老實講就係自己拎住本書讀果陣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n上Lecture 真係多鳩如<br />\n<br />\n老老實實<br />\n根本所有大專院校都係一門生意<br />\n咩degree , master degree 都係賺你錢咋傻閪<br />\n其他咩hd asso 就更加係明賺你錢，賺到(笑)<br />\n你班傻仔讀完就以為自己係明日之星<br />\n<br />\n咪撚 on9啦</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ffa286b3bd89d526ef63174637767fcb8eb5c516","tid":329992,"uid":49260,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-21T10:47:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><br />\n邊間會請鯨大？ 容我見識<br />\n佢老豆有deal?</blockquote><br />\n無問，唔講啦，行頭細<br />\n不過佢出國讀左個masters first hon</blockquote><br />\nFirst hon master<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n你讀緊中學？</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/21/183654_67a546ccbfa6ec03d22d8c18060538b2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F21%2F183654_67a546ccbfa6ec03d22d8c18060538b2.jpg&h=362a2c7c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n好心做人唔好咁井底啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n淨係識8間大學？<br />\n同埋係masters 唔係master<br />\n唔知邊個井底<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你19歲入ibank?<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n24</blockquote><br />\n睇你個底就知啦<br />\n一時就19歲未溝到女<br />\n一時就老闆in人</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 同弱智講野浪費時間"},{"pid":"95b35918f2f848d5eeeb9661fdd1a2148170d55f","tid":329992,"uid":71133,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-21T10:54:18.000Z","msg":"一睇內文陣酸味出晒黎，幾時有人講過畢業搵大錢，不嬲都係屌d仆街公司出得10k就想請個萬能大學生on99，要合理人工就叫想搵大錢?<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"616b053b949e3992e4f93e3da2e8d18bdb9da70e","tid":329992,"uid":11331,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-21T10:55:20.000Z","msg":"讀幾多master都冇用<br />\n除非