br />\n<br />\n政府工就全基本上係大學都一視同仁<br />\n升學就睇hon 話知你hku 定樹仁開大<br />\n<br />\n理論上 係Ou讀到first hon個人認為會比其他u既first hon更勁<br />\n<br />\n因為ou成績唔拉curve<br />\n過到3.5條線做first hon姐係你超過有一半學分係拎A 4.0<br />\n<br />\n而拎A係85分以上<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n利申：鯨大仔</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n原本個version 好似係恆大<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nBetween，pound of HSMC"},{"pid":"4ad17b02958762da431dc6a7a9387b4fa48e4b46","tid":329992,"uid":67551,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-21T12:26:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>唔會夠讀唔成書嗰啲黐線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n佢哋冇讀大學，出來幾年投身酒店、地產、保險 嗰堆，搵到快錢開始曬命<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 成日會有意無意曬下貴嘢，買股票贏幾多等等<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />永遠冇提衰嘢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />唔講以為佢係方展博<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n揾到快錢個班係可能冇有學歷個班長遠發展得咁好<br />\n但搵到快錢如果善用唔係鳩買野<br />\n正常係可以辛苦小幾年<br />\n不過搵到快錢係好似唔少人 但背後失敗既仲多<br />\n利申 搵到快錢買左樓 但想增值自己再轉行</blockquote><br />\n應該好少好似你咁<br />\n例如我識嗰個搵到錢唔係學實在嘢，而係買貴嘢/溝女，同聽啲咩投資講座兼學人玩股票<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />成日share埋啲positive memes同大講股票之道嗰啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />仲叫人跟佢學</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/21/152348_e316e62fa7f17d908a7acabfe3cee888.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F21%2F152348_e316e62fa7f17d908a7acabfe3cee888.jpg&h=968a7828&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n講真 讀到大學又點 咪又係搵得果萬頭<br />\n<br />\n呢個世界係錢搵錢 唔係人搵錢<br />\n<br />\n講真.....我早幾年買左層樓<br />\n<br />\n唔計升幅 收租都高過你份人工呀陰公</blockquote><br />\n下話<br />\n盛行咁巴閉？"},{"pid":"196dcfde133719a5e8083160fe41e2c1e151f587","tid":329992,"uid":13382,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-21T12:39:23.000Z","msg":"讀master 去擴闊人脈點睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e0954879c08d4951e05dc0066435fca29d204f91","tid":329992,"uid":36049,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-21T12:42:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>唔會夠讀唔成書嗰啲黐線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n佢哋冇讀大學，出來幾年投身酒店、地產、保險 嗰堆，搵到快錢開始曬命<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 成日會有意無意曬下貴嘢，買股票贏幾多等等<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />永遠冇提衰嘢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />唔講以為佢係方展博<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n揾到快錢個班係可能冇有學歷個班長遠發展得咁好<br />\n但搵到快錢如果善用唔係鳩買野<br />\n正常係可以辛苦小幾年<br />\n不過搵到快錢係好似唔少人 但背後失敗既仲多<br />\n利申 搵到快錢買左樓 但想增值自己再轉行</blockquote><br />\n應該好少好似你咁<br />\n例如我識嗰個搵到錢唔係學實在嘢，而係買貴嘢/溝女，同聽啲咩投資講座兼學人玩股票<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />成日share埋啲positive memes同大講股票之道嗰啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />仲叫人跟佢學</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/21/152348_e316e62fa7f17d908a7acabfe3cee888.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F21%2F152348_e316e62fa7f17d908a7acabfe3cee888.jpg&h=968a7828&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n講真 讀到大學又點 咪又係搵得果萬頭<br />\n<br />\n呢個世界係錢搵錢 唔係人搵錢<br />\n<br />\n講真.....我早幾年買左層樓<br />\n<br />\n唔計升幅 收租都高過你份人工呀陰公</blockquote><br />\n下話<br />\n盛行咁巴閉？</blockquote><br />\n陣冇u 讀既臭酸味酸能到😂😂"},{"pid":"43a5858edbec2a1030239d943c5f52dc766f1457","tid":329992,"uid":85359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-21T12:46:05.000Z","msg":"樓豬喺咪讀緊ive呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n喺人都知大學生fg人工不嬲低<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  但起碼吃香過啲<br />\nI大 恆管仔啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c3358d33b2608c63a344945c8f2ad024130f3298","tid":329992,"uid":41638,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-21T12:47:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>讀master 去擴闊人脈點睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n咁要睇下有無人想識毒撚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3436a944b191f7aa122e86688caed090646640f1","tid":329992,"uid":71133,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-21T12:49:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>唔會夠讀唔成書嗰啲黐線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n佢哋冇讀大學，出來幾年投身酒店、地產、保險 嗰堆，搵到快錢開始曬命<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 成日會有意無意曬下貴嘢，買股票贏幾多等等<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />永遠冇提衰嘢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />唔講以為佢係方展博<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n揾到快錢個班係可能冇有學歷個班長遠發展得咁好<br />\n但搵到快錢如果善用唔係鳩買野<br />\n正常係可以辛苦小幾年<br />\n不過搵到快錢係好似唔少人 但背後失敗既仲多<br />\n利申 搵到快錢買左樓 但想增值自己再轉行</blockquote><br />\n應該好少好似你咁<br />\n例如我識嗰個搵到錢唔係學實在嘢，而係買貴嘢/溝女，同聽啲咩投資講座兼學人玩股票<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />成日share埋啲positive memes同大講股票之道嗰啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />仲叫人跟佢學</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/21/152348_e316e62fa7f17d908a7acabfe3cee888.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F21%2F152348_e316e62fa7f17d908a7acabfe3cee888.jpg&h=968a7828&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n講真 讀到大學又點 咪又係搵得果萬頭<br 